description: Redevelopment of the former Zenith House site comprising the erection of buildings ranging from 2 to 16 storeys to provide 309 residential units, 1611sqm of Class B1 or D1 floorspace and 97sqm of Class A1 or Class A3 floorspace along with a landscaped courtyard, provision of 218 car parking spaces and 349 cycle spaces, vehicular access from Colindeep Lane and pedestrian access from Colindale Avenue.
